      "created_at": "2021-08-12T17:16:46.163Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi Alex,</p>\n<p>I have a problem when I do a workout in EGR mode. The power never reaches the power target, it\u2019s 20-30 watts below so to reach it I need to shift gears or increase the cadence but again after 10-15 seconds with that new configuration the power drops down again. I have a Elite Direto XR and use the Trainer app with an Ipad.</p>\n<p>II don\u2019t know if that could be a set-up error from my side or a application bug, so please, could you help to to fix it?</p>\n<p>Thank you.</p>",
