      "created_at": "2021-08-12T19:38:05.728Z",
      "cooked": "<p>To me this sounds like a problem with your trainer. Have you used your trainer with any other ERG app? Like Zwift in ERG? You might want to try a firmware update.  For sure we have many direto users that don\u2019t have a problem. It sounds like you tried this and I don\u2019t think this is the problem based on what you described but make sure you are in a middle gear.</p>\n<p>The way it works is we tell your trainer to target 150w and if it does not hit 150w it should not be our issue but if it is somehow if you wanted to spend a little time with my developer, I am sure we could resolve it.</p>",
